public override long Length { get { return this.filter.Length; } }

public override long Position { get { return this.filter.Position; } set { this.filter.Position = value; } } } 
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`You can put what ever you want inside the if statement of the `}<strong parentName="p">{`Flush`}</strong>{` method. In my case, I remove all script of the file, replace them with a comment and finally put all scripts at the end of the file, just before the closing Html tag.`}</p>
